  npcVisitFlavors:
  - speaks of the deep water, and what listens from below.
  - tells you which plants the bog respects, and which ones it takes back.
  - seems to know the mood of the weather before it arrives.
  npcExchangeFlavors:
  - offers mushrooms from the deep edges of the fen. Foraged, not bought.
  - draws a small bell from their pack, still carrying the weight of what it was.
